          <tr>
          <td valign=top align=left>
          <font size="-1" face="Lucida Grande,Arial,Verdana,sans-serif" color=#555555>
This clip was found on the YouTube channel of Apollo Systems HK in 2023.
It shows the AR-924 pager in operation and highlights its
<a href="#features"><span data-balloon-pos="up" aria-label="Jump to: unique fea&shy;tures">unique fea&shy;tures</span></a>, like the improved user inter&shy;face and the
85 day battery life.
Note that the name of the origi&shy;nal manufacturer &ndash; Gold Apollo &ndash; is used
in the video, although in reality it was Apollo Systems HK that was
responsible for the design and sales.
<br />
